show.title: The Natural Nurse

title: Energy Medicine Begins with Water
content:
Host, Eugene Zampieron, ND, www.drznaturally.com, interviews Dr. Norman SuHu. Dr. <!--more--> Suhu is a naturopathic doctor with specialized training in Biosyntonie, Carroll Food Intolerance testing, hydrotherapy, acupuncture, and homeopathy and keeps regular office hours in his New York City and Glen Cove, Long Island offices.
 Dr SuHu is one of the few senior practitioners of Biosyntonie in the United States and regularly teaches health practitioners this method of energy healing in New York and by invitation numerous times in Switzerland, San Francisco, Los Angeles, Santa Barbara, and Boulder.
 Contact: www.songofhealth.com
